source.name: 2010 Healthcare and Family Services Provider Fields (ReadMe)
source.description:
http://www2.illinois.gov/hfs/agency/Transparency/Pages/default.aspx
This Read Me file is intended to accompany Healthcare and Family Services' Provider data set, which contains information on Illinois Medicaid healthcare services providers (physicians, nurses, and many others). The provider data set is available on data.illinois.gov and we encourage all data users to use the two uploads together. 
Please visit HFS's Transparency webpage at http://www2.illinois.gov/hfs/agency/Transparency/Pages/default.aspx for more information on the data we provide.
